summary: This is the ultimate biology review video. Trying to review all of biology in less than 90 minutes is an insane task. Im going to go over the most important points in this video and well do this in the following order we will start by talking about the cell and whats in it of course there is the nucleus with DNA and the cytoplasm with the organelles. Then we will talk about reproduction mitosis and meiosis after this embryogenesis and the fetal circulation followed by the nervous system.
